Salve may refer to any of the following:

  • River Salve, marks the border between Misthalin and Morytania
  • Salve shard, a crystal cut from deep inside the Haunted Mine
  • Salve amulet, provides a boost in combat while attacking undead monsters

    • Salve amulet(i), provides a boost in combat while attacking undead monsters
